3.2. simulation workﬂow setting

          KNIME ,a data mining software,is used for simulation experiment and the simulation of fault diagnosis is realized
       by constructing workﬂows.
       The implementation steps as fellow:

            • 500 oil-immersed transformer fault data for database are read;
            • With the normalization processing ,this data are divided into sample data and test data randomly;
            • Probabilistic neural network learning is used to learn of the data, and the fault prediction model for failure
              prediction is to be establish;
